Missing Keys
------------

<div class="fragment">
\begin{spec}
λ> :m +Data.Map
λ> let m = fromList [ ("haskell"    , "lazy")
                    , ("javascript" , "eager")]

λ> m ! "haskell"
"lazy"
\end{spec}
</div>

<br>

<div class="fragment">
\begin{spec}
λ> m ! "clojure"
"*** Exception: key is not in the map
\end{spec}
