Segmentation Faults
-------------------

<div class="fragment">
\begin{spec}
λ> :m +Data.Vector
λ> let v = fromList ["haskell", "javascript"]
λ> unsafeIndex v 0
"haskell"
\end{spec}
</div>

<div class="fragment">
<br>
\begin{spec}
λ> V.unsafeIndex v 3

'ghci' terminated by signal SIGSEGV ...
\end{spec}
</div>

