"HeartBleeds"
-------------


\begin{spec}
λ> :m + Data.Text Data.Text.Unsafe
λ> let t = pack "StrangeLoop"
λ> takeWord16 5 t
"Stran"
\end{spec}

<br>

<div class="fragment">
Memory overflows **leaking secrets**...

<br>

\begin{spec}
λ> takeWord16 20 t
"StrangeLoop\1912\3148\NUL\15928\2486\SOH\NUL"
\end{spec}
</div>

